        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">Steps to reproduce:</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.2">1 Open Calc.</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.3">2 Open the Function Wizard using any valid method.</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.4">3 Select AVERAGEIF or AVERAGEIFS by either single-clicking or double-clicking on the function name in the list.</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.5">4 Press the Help button in the dialog.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">Current behavior: LibreOffice crashes.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="5">
            <sentence id="5.1">Expected behavior: Help files should open.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
